<plot>Ted Husing ran out of ideas and put together this one-reeler about umpires and referees in the world of sports. Ted details the activities of relay umpires at track-and-field event, and then moves on to basketball referees, baseball umpires, football referees and umpires, and wrestling referees. No, they did not 'rassle; they refereed wrestling matches.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?221925</url></doc>
